{"tid":781230,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人同我一樣同前度分手好後悔","createTime":"2018-08-15T17:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-15T17:51:12.000Z","uid":54088,"like":0,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"574acad955096e1fe143a839359f865ffe652fc5","tid":781230,"uid":54088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:30:20.000Z","msg":"訓唔著想開個post<br />\n我知巴打你地一定話我仆街<br />\n話說同前女友散佐就黎兩年<br />\n明明分佐手我會得到解脫<br />\n其實呢兩年黎我一直都放吾低<br />\n佢係一個對感情認真 善良嘅女仔<br />\n一開始佢會關心我覺得佢有種成熟既味道先同佢<br />\n一齊 乜都幫我唸囇 慢慢佢依賴佐我 我就覺得煩 <br />\n耐佐太平凡覺得對住佢無囇感覺 成日制造機會分手<br />\n佢仲話想同我過世我好驚 我認我未挽夠丫 <br />\n我同佢根本就唔岩過咩世<br />\n開始尋找刺激感同其他女仔瞹昧<br />\n無意比佢發現 佢無踢爆我 我知佢夜晚偷偷地喊<br />\n佢無同情佢反而對佢呢個舉動好反感<br />\n我又不停冷落佢嫌棄佢 最後佢終於忍唔住要分手 話對我好失望 浪費佢對我既真心 之後佢就好似消失佐咁 無人嘅時候會懷念佢對我嘅好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔夠一個月我就同佐第二條女一齊<br />\n點知遇著個思想幼稚最后都係無終而疾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最近佢前女友佢又出現反 係麥當當撞反佢拖住條仔<br />\n佢瘦佐 識得打扮 有佐當初無既果種氣質 <br />\n我見到佢望佐我一眼無回頭<br />\n我宜家好后悔 好后悔同佢分手 我傷得佢好深 我都知反唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可吾可以揾人鬧醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果有多次機會我想好好珍惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我不配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3e9ea7ee9460669b2a10e12732b476a6ecb4453","tid":781230,"uid":51250,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},{"pid":"4f6d24d7e89a6d258abdecda55ea73f87646cec9","tid":781230,"uid":197135,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b3e9ea7ee9460669b2a10e12732b476a6ecb4453","tid":781230,"uid":51250,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:31:05.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:31:37.000Z","msg":"挽佢老母"},{"pid":"1bb266ca5db9e714d3e516935c5ebb47a0d163ee","tid":781230,"uid":187076,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:32:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/16/013247_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F16%2F013247_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=04c60826&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d91eee34d2631dc4fe5744d20a97c353ce72867","tid":781230,"uid":126841,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:41:11.000Z","msg":"丫你老母咩讀多3年書先再開post啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56877fa5a6eaf0cbea80d242743d7f63ae84f2ed","tid":781230,"uid":6031,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T17:51:12.000Z","msg":"吾<br />\n丫<br />\n挽<br />\n反<br />\n<br />\n唔係無終而疾，係無疾而終呀<br />\n成語唔係靠背係有典故架，咩撚嘢無終而疾呀？有腦都知調轉咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n讀下書啦5p仔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}